#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.91"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.91:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.91:0.2"
msgid "10. Asuravagga "
msgstr "10. Demons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.91:0.3"
msgid "91. Asurasutta "
msgstr "91. Demons "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.91:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.91:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol>
msgctxt "an4.91:1.3"
msgid "Asuro asuraparivāro, asuro devaparivāro, devo asuraparivāro, devo devaparivāro. "
msgstr "~A demon surrounded by demons, ~a demon surrounded by gods, ~a god surrounded by demons, and ~a god surrounded by gods. "

#. HTML: </ol><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.91:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo asuro hoti asuraparivāro? "
msgstr "And how is a person a demon surrounded by demons? "

msgctxt "an4.91:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo dussīlo hoti pāpadhammo, parisāpissa hoti dussīlā pāpadhammā. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is unethical, of bad character, and their followers are the same. "

msgctxt "an4.91:2.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo asuro hoti asuraparivāro. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a demon surrounded by demons. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.91:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo asuro hoti devaparivāro? "
msgstr "And how is a person a demon surrounded by gods? "

msgctxt "an4.91:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo dussīlo hoti pāpadhammo, parisā ca khvassa hoti sīlavatī kalyāṇadhammā. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is unethical, of bad character, but their followers are ethical, of good character. "

msgctxt "an4.91:3.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo asuro hoti devaparivāro. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a demon surrounded by gods. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.92, sc4
msgctxt "an4.91:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo devo hoti asuraparivāro? "
msgstr "And how is a person a god surrounded by demons? "

msgctxt "an4.91:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sīlavā hoti kalyāṇadhammo, parisā ca khvassa hoti dussīlā pāpadhammā. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is ethical, of good character, but their followers are unethical, of bad character. "

msgctxt "an4.91:4.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo devo hoti asuraparivāro. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a god surrounded by demons. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.91:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo devo hoti devaparivāro? "
msgstr "And how is a person a god surrounded by gods? "

msgctxt "an4.91:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sīlavā hoti kalyāṇadhammo, parisāpissa hoti sīlavatī kalyāṇadhammā. "
msgstr "It’s when a person is ethical, of good character, and their followers are the same. "

msgctxt "an4.91:5.3"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo devo hoti, devaparivāro. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is a god surrounded by gods. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.91:5.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.91:5.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
